entries.journal_entry_description: Qakkee believes he's the greatest hunter in the galaxy. Prove that you are his equal!
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Help avenge Qakkee's lost body parts and kill the monstrosity Sawtooth. He's rumored to live in 'the Dead Forest' or Kkowir on the planet Kashyyyk. If you manage to kill him, return one of his eyeballs to Qakkee as proof.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: You have done what no one else has and defeated the monster Sawtooth! Return to Qakkee with the eyeball.
